content.rendered:
Directed by Chethan Kumar

Written by Chethan Kumar

Cast Puneeth Rajkumar (Santhosh Kumar). Priya Anand (Nisha Gayakwad). Meka Srikanth (Vijay Gayakwad). Anu Prabhakar. R. Sarathkumar (as Sarath Kumar). Madhusudhan Rao. Mukesh Rishi. Adithya Menon. Rangayana Raghu. Avinash. Sadhu Kokila. Thilak Shekar. Chikkanna. Suchendra Prasad. Padmaja Rao. Ketan Karande. John Kokken. Rukh Nabeel. Raghavendra Rajkumar. Rachita Ram. Ashika Ranganath. Shivarajkumar. Sreeleela. Sal Yusuf (voice)

Languages Kannada

Producers Kishore Pathikonda

Production Kishore Productions
